{
  "id": "adv_main_01_09_02",
  "title": "星見編2章33話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私達の、新しい衣装……？\nもう完成したんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? We’re getting new costumes?\nAre they already finished?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、衣装の製作はこれからだ\nでもいくつか候補になるデザインはあがったらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ costume construction will come later.\nBut they’ve got a few potential designs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとに？　見たい見たーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I wanna see them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "私も見てみたい！\nどんなデザインなのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see them‚ too!\nI wonder what the designs look like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.691088358561196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まだ、あくまで候補だよ。ここからさらに固めていく\n……そこで、だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These are still candidates for costumes. We’ll finalize it later.\nAnd that’s where you come in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5076189994812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "各グループから代表で一人、デザイン打ち合わせに\n参加して意見をもらえないか、ってお願いされてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They asked if each group would send one representative\nto come to the design meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.963855044047044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私達着る側の意見を取り入れて、グループごとの\n個性を出していきたい……ってことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ they’re incorporating our opinions‚ the people wearing the costumes‚\nbecause they want to bring out each group’s uniqueness… is that it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.263855044047055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ！　そういうことでしたらとーぜん！\n私が直々に乗り込む――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah-hah! If that’s what they want‚ then‚ naturally!\nI shall personally hop on board!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.23052171071373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、グループのセンターでもある\n琴乃とさくらでいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ why not have the centers of both groups go?\nKotono and Sakura‚ yeah?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.681784982578776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ！　私の話を最後まで聞きなさい！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Let me finish what I was saying!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.681784982578776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "でも……打ち合わせって言っても\nデザインについてなんて、何を話したらいいか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… you said it’s a meeting‚\nbut I don’t really know about costume design. I wouldn’t know what to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.16139954238815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "なら、前もってみんなで話し合って\nイメージや希望をまとめておけばいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why don’t we all talk it over beforehand‚\nand brainstorm a list of images and things we want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.50999382644578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、それなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that might work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.50999382644578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "あの……その前に、ちょっといいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ before we decide on anything‚ can I make a suggestion?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.77192131191178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうした、沙季",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What’s up‚ Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.52752224117204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.99319123734716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "確かにさくらちゃんや琴乃ちゃんはセンターで\n適任とは思うのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True‚ since Sakura and Kotono are the centers‚\nthey would be appropriate choices‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.05985790401382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ今回は、他の人に任せてみても\nいいのではないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but this might be why we should let someone else handle it.\nDon’t you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.38444246036221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だな。実は俺も少し考えてたんだ\nセンターは顔をすぐ覚えてもらえるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I do. Actually‚ I was thinking the same thing.\nThe center-girls are easily recognizable‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.75110912702884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ今回は、他のメンバーの存在感を\nしっかりアピールするのもいいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "which is precisely why the other members need some time in the spotlight.\nI think we need to help sell everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.88444246036217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……それは言えてるかも\nけど、誰にお願いするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… Yeah‚ I think that’s a good point.\nBut who should we send?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.78444246036221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "でしたら、やっぱり月ストは私が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you need a representative from Moon Tempest‚ then I shall—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.45110912702889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "私が出席してもいいですか？\n月ストの衣装打ち合わせ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "May I attend\nthe Moon Tempest costume meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.13444255572952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。確かに沙季は適任かもしれないな\n琴乃達も、それでいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I do think you may be the most appropriate choice‚ Saki.\nKotono‚ are you okay with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.50110922239617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私は……私が行くよりは\n沙季さんに任せた方がいいって思うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think… instead of sending me‚\nleaving this in Saki’s capable hands would be better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.90110922239616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "私もー\n打ち合わせって、眠くなっちゃうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree!\nMeetings and stuff make me sleepy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.56777588906283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私も異論はないです。すずちゃんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no objections either. What about you‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.70110922239616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "し……仕方ありませんわね！　私ばかり\n目立っても月ストのためになりませんから……ぐぬぬ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ it can’t be helped‚ can it! If I am the only one\nwho stands out‚ that will do no favors to Moon Tempest… *sniffle*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.5821750360965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "よし\nそれじゃあサニピの方は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good.\nThen‚ for Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7737396596112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、千紗……一緒にやってみない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Chisa‚ want to go with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.24040632627788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
